  "texts": [
    "For the healthy subjects, UPDRS-III and H &Y values are denoted by n/a.",
    "Samuel et al.",
    "37 suggested that to test the effectiveness of a newly developed machine learning method, it is a good approach to choose dataset(s) that have been extensively tested.",
    "Thus, our choice of datasets in this paper was based on the facts discussed in 37.",
    "We propose a two-stage feature selection and classification method to detect PD using replicated voice data and various voice records."
  ]
}